Package ardat.tree

Class ArchiveEntity

java.lang.Object
ardat.tree.ArchiveEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, AutoCloseable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArchiveEntityDecorator, DirectoryEntity, FileEntity
public abstract class ArchiveEntity extends Object implements Closeable
ArchiveEntity is an abstract class, which stores information about a file descriptor. ArchiveEntity is a component participant of the Composite pattern. Every ArchiveEntity object can have children or a parent. If an ArchiveEntity doesn't have a parent it considered a root of the tree. If an ArchiveEntity can't have children it considered a leaf.
